"Spanish Official": José Rizal, you are accused of inspiring rebellion against Spain.
Rizal: I have only written to expose injustice.
"Spanish Official": Your writings have influenced many.
Rizal: If they awaken the people, then they have served their purpose.
josephinebracken: There must be a way to save you.
Rizal:  Do not lose hope. What matters is the cause we fought for.
We will not forget you.
Rizal:  I die with a clear conscience.
"Spanish Official": The sentence is death.
Rizal:  I am ready to face it.